title: The Disappearance of Haruhi Suzumiya
description:
The Disappearance of Haruhi Suzumiya


         Audio:English dub

                        Summary

             Ten days before Christmas, it seemed like another ordinary

             day for the SOS Brigade; Haruhi came up with another one of

             her crazy ideas to hold a Christmas party in the club room.

             But then things got weirder from there... The next day Kyon

             woke up to a world in which Haruhi didn't exist and no one 

             besides him had any memory of her. How can someone like 

             Haruhi Suzumiya, who's supposed to be center of the 

             universe, just vanish?
